# Q1 2026 Product Strategy Review

::summary
CloudSurf is executing a multi-product strategy with TaskSurf as the lead product.
Revenue target is $5K MRR by end of Q2, driven by TaskSurf subscriptions and
Wavesite upsells. Patent portfolio provides defensive moat with 16 families filed.
::

