::callout[type=tip title="Revenue Priority"]
Focus engineering effort on TaskSurf billing activation. Every week of delay
costs approximately $2K in potential MRR based on pipeline conversations.
::

## Key Decisions

::decision[status=accepted date="2026-02-08"]
Absorb CloudSurf HQ into TaskSurf. The standalone dashboard adds maintenance
overhead without differentiated value. AI chat, agent personas, and strategy
features become TaskSurf premium tier capabilities.
::

::decision[status=proposed date="2026-02-10"]
Evaluate SST v3 migration for TaskSurf backend. Amplify Gen 2 is blocking
custom domain configuration and advanced caching. Migration cost estimated
at 2-3 engineering days.
::

